                                                    <h2 class="mt-20">Links & buttons <a href=""
                                                            id="Links-and-buttons" class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h2>
                                                    <p>
                                                    By adding .list-group-item-action, you may use a>s or button>s to create actionable list group items with hover, disabled, and active states. To make sure list groups comprised of non-interactive components (such <li>s or <div>s) don't offer a click or tap affordance, we segregate these pseudo-classes.
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p>Be sure to <strong>not use the
                                                            standard</strong> <code>.btn</code> <strong>classes
                                                            here</strong>.</p>

