                                                    <h2 class="mt-20">Numbered <a href="" id="Numbered"
                                                            class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h2>
                                                    <p>
                                                    To opt into numbered list group items, add the <code>.list-group-numbered</code> modifier class (and omit the <code>&lt;ol&gt;</code> element, if desired). To enable more customisation and better placement inside list group items, numbers are generated using CSS (as opposed to an <code>&lt;ol&gt;</code>s default browser styling).
                                                    </p>
                                                    <p><code>Counter-reset</code> on the <code>&lt;ol&gt;</code> is used to create numbers, which are then stylized and placed on the <code>&lt;li&gt;</code> with counter-increment and content using <code>::before pseudo-element</code>.
                                                    </p>
