                                                <h2 class="mt-20">Fade effect <a href="" id="Fade-effect"
                                                        class="opacity-0 hover-1">#</a></h2>
                                                <p>
                                                Add <code>.fade</code> to each <code>.tab-pane</code> to have the tabs panel fade in. For the original content to be displayed, the first tab pane also has to have show.
                                                </p>

                                                <!-- code -->

                                                <div class="code_bg rounded p-3">
                                                    <button class="btn btn-outline-primary float-end" id="copyButton24"
